column5: Hey Guy's, they kicked me out of the Hosp. today. I think they had had enough of me. Had a Bone Scan done today and I have to go back for a Colon probe.   The actual operation itself went fine, every thing working as it should.. Just have to wait the results and  start a plan of action. Ive always been a fighter, so between Jackie and Me, we will kick this thing in the donkey.  "Donkey ??  Would really like to thank everyone for your messages, kind thoughts and good wishes. Gonna print them off, to help in low times, Many thanks once again  P.s.. I really hope the new Hosp. works out a lot better than this old one.  UGH!!!!!!
So glad your back and okay Jack.  I was thinking about you.  This is great news  Joey
Go gettem!!  Iveb een thinking of ya!!
Good to see yer home again Jack.I cant believe they kicked you out so quickly. Joe
Good stuff Jack, glad to see you back up and still fighting  Maureen
Good to hear your back onto the route to recovery!  Stan
Damn glad to have ya back Jack!!!   ... as for the colon probe, we can do that right here!!!... now bend over and touch your toes.................
Glad to here your doing great Jack!
I wish you a very speedy recovery !!!!
Glad to hear your back home Jack....  Hope everything continue's down the good path of recovery....
Welcome back Jack! I hope it all goes well!
Glad for you to hear that that's over with  I hope the results are favourable and the test up the back end   goes well for you too
Good having you back aboard Jack !!
Welcome back Jack!!! Get well soon and stay well always!!!  GM
Very very nice to see you back home Jack. It must also be a great relief for Jackie as it is for all of us here. Welcome back, my friend.
Glad your home...now just do what they tell you and stay positive positive positive!!!!!!

I guess you aren't going to miss your old (90's) roomates, but then it is not every day we get called "junior" at our age...  Glad to hear you are home...now we got to beat this thing with whatever it takes...
Ya just can't keep a good man down.  Glad to see you're back home and prayers for the test results.
Glad to hear some good news  Best of luck  for continued success!
Glad to here your back home !!!!!!
Many Thanks once again, folks!  This OFC Family will get anyone, through anything. PHENOMINAL.!!!!!!!!

Nanook hope all turns out good for you. so between Jackie and Me, we will kick this thing in the donkey.  "Donkey ??  ------ you've got the right attitude... keep your chin up and keep thinking positive.    Dann
